msDesc.head: Liturgical works; Iceland, Germany, England, Hollandc. 1200, ss. XIII-XVI

msContents.summary: Fragments of Latin parchment manuscripts found in the bindings of manuscripts in the Arnamagnæan Collection.

source.p: Catalogued by EW-J based on the information in Merete Geert Andersen's catalogue.
